sequenceDiagram
    participant Kafka as Kafka Brokers<br/>9092/TCP SASL_SSL
    participant KP as kafka-processor<br/>Python 3.12
    participant VHub as model-validation-hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant API as api-client<br/>Python 3.12
    participant Enrich as enrich_models.py
    participant FS as Local Filesystem<br/>data/
    participant Build as Dockerfile.konflux<br/>Container Build
    participant Init as Init Container<br/>/app/benchmarks
    participant Volume as Shared Volume
    participant MC as model-catalog<br/>Main Container

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over Kafka,FS: Flow 1: Kafka Ingestion Pipeline
        Kafka->>KP: CDC messages (5 topics)<br/>SASL_SSL / SCRAM-SHA-512
        KP->>KP: Parse CDC envelopes<br/>Deduplicate records
        KP->>KP: Apply transforms<br/>(OverallAccuracy, HardwareConfig)
        KP->>FS: Write JSON/NDJSON files<br/>provider/model hierarchy
    end

    rect rgb(255, 248, 240)
        Note over VHub,FS: Flow 2: API Ingestion Pipeline
        API->>VHub: GET /api/v1/providers<br/>TLS (custom CA)
        VHub-->>API: Provider list
        API->>VHub: GET /api/v1/models<br/>TLS (custom CA)
        VHub-->>API: Model metadata
        API->>VHub: GET /api/v1/evaluations<br/>TLS (custom CA)
        VHub-->>API: Evaluation scores
        API->>VHub: GET /api/v1/performances<br/>TLS (custom CA)
        VHub-->>API: Performance metrics
        API->>VHub: GET /api/v1/validations<br/>TLS (custom CA)
        VHub-->>API: Validation results
        API->>API: Post-process data
        API->>FS: Write JSON/NDJSON files<br/>provider/model hierarchy
    end

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over Enrich,FS: Flow 3: Data Enrichment
        Enrich->>Enrich: Read cold-start-vram-data/*.json
        Enrich->>FS: Merge cold-start, VRAM,<br/>image-size into metadata.json
    end

    rect rgb(248, 240, 255)
        Note over FS,MC: Flow 4: Container Build & Deployment
        FS->>Build: COPY data/ → /app/benchmarks
        Build->>Init: Container image built<br/>UBI9-minimal base
        Init->>Volume: Copy benchmark data<br/>to shared volume
        Volume->>MC: model-catalog reads<br/>benchmark data
    end
